\begin_layout Standard
Growth is given by:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
g=\eta\left(x_{e,\omega}\mu_{e,\omega}+x_{e,1}\mu_{e,1}+\lambda x_{I}\mu_{1}\right)
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
pause
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Inventors' productivity (growth per inventor):
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{g}{L^{RD}}=\eta\frac{x_{e,\omega}\mu_{e,\omega}+x_{e,1}\mu_{e,1}+\lambda x_{I}\mu_{1}}{\zeta\left(\omega x_{e,\omega}\mu_{e,\omega}+x_{e,1}\mu_{e,1}\right)+\alpha_{I}\frac{x_{I}^{\gamma}}{\gamma}\mu_{1}}.
\]

\end_inset


