\begin_layout Itemize
Inventors' market clearing:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
L^{RD,s}\left(w^{RD}\right) & =\sum_{i=1,2}\left\lbrace \mu_{1,i}\left(w^{RD}\right)\alpha_{I}\frac{x_{I,i}^{\gamma}\left(w^{RD}\right)}{\gamma}+\right.\\
 & \left.+\mu_{\omega,i}\left(w^{RD}\right)\zeta_{i}\omega_{i}x_{e,\omega,i}\left(w^{RD}\right)+\mu_{1,e,i}\left(w^{RD}\right)\zeta_{i}x_{e,1,i}\left(w^{RD}\right)\right\rbrace 
\end{align*}

\end_inset


